    <section identifier="/ca-mountain-view/chapter-1/article-ii/section-sec.-1.25"
             temporalId="sSEC_ 1_25">
      <num>SEC. 1.25</num>
      <heading>Judicial review</heading>
      <content>
        <p>Any person subject to a decision of the hearing officer may obtain judicial review
               of the decision in the superior court pursuant to the provisions of California Government
               Code Section 53069.4.</p>
        <p>(Ord. No. 12.02, 7/23/02.)</p>
      </content>
    </section>
